\begin_layout Standard
A few specifics about this SPI configuration:
 we use 
\family typewriter
SPI_SUB_MODE_3 
\family default
(line 16) to ignore the default chip select and ensure we are using the chip select defined in Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
