noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

.
 We also enable the interna SPI pin select,
 which is defined at pin 50 (line 31).
 This ensures that the internal SPI API plays nice;
 we found that if it was not enabled,
 even though it remains unused,
 functions like 
\family typewriter
MAP_SPITransfer()
\family default
will hang up and never return from their calls,
 probably because these SPI read/write functions are expecting Pin 50 to be enabled.
 If we enable it behind the scenes,
 we can proceed with our CS config at Pin 2.
\end_layout

