\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We loop through the entire ASCII font array,
 using 
\family typewriter
PIXEL_WIDTH
\family default
 in our iterations to ensure the characters are sufficiently large spaced out (otherwise they would overlap).
 
\family typewriter
drawChar()
\family default
 is sufficient for our needs to draw each of these,
 and that is about the extent of this implementation.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Hello,
 world!
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 is pretty similar,
