After shifting around some pins,
 we're ready to get started.
 All of the SPI configuration and OLED initialization is effectively the same,
 with the exception of changing the pin values being used (for Reset and OLEDCS).
 We also need to initialize I2C,
 which is simply calling 
\family typewriter
I2C_IF_Open(I2C_MASTER_MODE_FST)
\family default
.
 Now,
 the code which makes the pitching ball is below.
 Let's walk through it:
